\pard\plain\ltrpar\qc\s28\itap0{\s28\f2\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\qj\s28\itap0{\s28\f0\fs24\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch In this assignment you will create an application that performs multipass antialiasing.  The algorithm computes multiple samples distributed around each display pixel and weights (filters) these into one final value.  A screen space offset is added to the transformed vertex coordinates of each triangle to produce the sample distribution.  }{\s28\f0\fs24\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\qj\s28\itap0{\s28\f2\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
