\pard\plain\ltrpar\qj\s28\itap0{\s28\f0\fs24\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch Your application sets up multiple Renderers and Displays -- one pair for each sample in the table.  Each Renderer is initialized with a different offset and display to write into.  All triangles are sent to all renderers.  }{\s28\f0\fs24\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
